Class Destination

  • java.lang.Object
    • Destination

  • public class Destination
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Destination represents the information regarding the available locations for shipment/delivery

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Destination(java.lang.String reg, Parcel par)
      This constructor receives the intended region/destination and the parcel (specifically the size, which will be used to compute the service fee)
